summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions passed by shareholders via poll voting.  
- **Key Approved Items**:  
  - Issuance of Consideration Shares (Resolution 1) – 97.82% approval  
  - Creation & issuance of Performance Shares (Resolutions 2 & 3) – 95.44% and 94.40% approval  
  - Debt Conversion Shares (Resolution 4) – 96.48% approval  
  - Placement Shares (Resolution 5) – 97.11% approval  
  - Issuance of Lead Manager Options (Resolution 6) – 94.97% approval  
  - Director Options (Resolutions 7a-7d) – 96.21% approval for each director  
  - Director Placement Shares (Resolution 8) – 96.98% approval  

*No material impact on trading or capital structure beyond disclosed shareholder approvals for issuances.*
